snippet.title: Amber Heard & Richard Dawkins - Atheism, Secularism, Coming Out, Hollywood - VIP Arizona 2019
snippet.description:
Amber Heard answers question on awareness of atheism, secularism, humanism, Hollywood, and coming out as atheist in public. A VIP asked why others in Hollywood are not promoting Atheism like Amber. - From Richard Dawkins & Amber Heard event in Mesa, Arizona on October 16, 2019...  Being atheist "probably saved my life."

#AmberHeard #RichardDawkins #Atheism #Secularism #Humanism #ComingOut #Hollywood #VIP #Agnostic
